  "version_pin_rationale": "sway 1.7-1 is the jammy universe release build. Used as the DE-H1 Wayland compositor stand-in for Hyprland (which is NOT in jammy and ships only source tarballs upstream; see docs/wayland-de-hyprland.md 'Why sway (not Hyprland)'). Both sway and Hyprland are wlroots-based Wayland compositors with the same DE0-G dependency footprint; the swap is invisible to the rest of the rootfs. swaybg 1.0-2build1 is sway's wallpaper helper (Depends: in the sway .deb). swaybar, swaymsg, swaynag are all in the sway .deb. The /etc/sway/config planted by the .deb is a 4 KB documented template; DE-H1's build script OVERWRITES it with the translated /etc/hyprland.conf bindings."
